::Feline::

She smiled and shifted her wieght onto her other foot. "I'll scout around 
since I have a choice in the matter." she said softly.  She nodded to him, 
knowing he was one of the few bots that could resist her charms. After all, 
she was build to seek, seduce and destroy her prey. She was extremely good 
at it. "What's the quadrant that you want checked out commander?"
